de.mrapp.android.dialog.model

Interface HeaderDialogDecorator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Dialog
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ButtonBarDialog, HeaderDialog, ListDialog, ValidateableDialog
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractButtonBarDialog, AbstractHeaderDialog, AbstractHeaderDialogFragment, AbstractListDialog, AbstractValidateableDialog, HeaderDialogDecorator, MaterialDialog, ProgressDialog, WizardDialog

    public interface HeaderDialogDecorator
extends Dialog
    Defines the interface of a decorator, which allows to modify the view hierarchy of a dialog, which is designed according to Android 5's Material Design guidelines even on pre-Lollipop devices and may contain a header, must implement.
    Since:
    3.2.0
